title: ISic000688. I.Sicily inscription 000688
body:
Facsimile Images

Apparatus criticus

  • Manganaro refrained from transcribing the text, and it has not been located since.

translation

commentary

No text has been recorded, but it is clear from the poor photo in Manganaro 1989 that there is a Latin text on the stone, at least one line long, but in a poor state of preservation.

bibliography

  • Manganaro 1989 164 no. 17 fig.17 https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001831
  • Fasolo 2013 90 no. 54 https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002011
